unfav
Kevin Cantu <me@kevincantu.org>
September 2011

STATUS:
I'm currently writing the part which 
deletes old favorites on Twitter...

BUILD:
$ cabal-dev add-source /code/askitter
$ cabal-dev install askitter
$ cabal-dev configure
$ cabal-dev build
$ ./dist/build/unfav/unfav -h
unfav
  -g         --generate       generate, then save a Twitter API token
                              (requires you specify a KEY and SECRET, too)
  -k KEY     --key=KEY        a consumer key for this app to use
  -s SECRET  --secret=SECRET  a consumer secret for this app to use
  -x         --clean          clean up: remove the saved the access token
  -h         --help           display this help
  -v         --version        display version


